{"id":3586,"date":"2015-08-26T06:42:35","date_gmt":"2015-08-26T06:42:35","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/ezrankings.org\/blog\/?p=3586"},"modified":"2021-03-03T10:33:38","modified_gmt":"2021-03-03T10:33:38","slug":"know-the-hidden-social-media-features-to-help-your-small-business-flourish","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"\/blog\/know-the-hidden-social-media-features-to-help-your-small-business-flourish\/","title":{"rendered":"Know the Hidden Social Media Features to Help Your Small Business Flourish"},"content":{"rendered":"<p align=\"justify\">Every small business should have a <a class=\"ezurl\" href=\"\/blog\/double-social-media-following-easy-steps\/\">social media strategy to build up followers<\/a> and social shares with unique content and good management. However, you need to know a few hidden social media features to help your business thrive.<\/p>\n<p align=\"justify\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-7140\" src=\"https:\/\/ezranking.s3.eu-west-2.amazonaws.com\/ezrankings\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/09\/07120945\/social-media-marketing.jpg\" alt=\"social-media-marketing\" width=\"848\" height=\"403\" srcset=\"https:\/\/ezranking.s3.eu-west-2.amazonaws.com\/ezrankings\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/09\/07120945\/social-media-marketing.jpg 848w, https:\/\/ezranking.s3.eu-west-2.amazonaws.com\/ezrankings\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/09\/07120945\/social-media-marketing-300x143.jpg 300w, https:\/\/ezranking.s3.eu-west-2.amazonaws.com\/ezrankings\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/09\/07120945\/social-media-marketing-768x365.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 848px) 100vw, 848px\" \/><\/p>\n<div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_69 counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-grey ez-toc-container-direction\">\n<div class=\"ez-toc-title-container\">\n<p class=\"ez-toc-title \" >Table of Contents<\/p>\n<span class=\"ez-toc-title-toggle\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn